Package: socialchoicelab
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Social Choice Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("SocialChoiceLab Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "maintainer@socialchoicelab.example")
Description: Spatial and general social choice analysis: distance and loss
    functions, majority preference, winsets, uncovered set, Copeland scores,
    preference profiles, and positional voting rules. Calls the pre-built
    libscs_api shared library via the C ABI; no C++ compilation required.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
Imports:
    R6 (>= 2.5.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: libscs_api shared library (set SCS_LIB_PATH to its
    directory, or place it on the system library path)
